## 5. Indexing Strategy

### `users`
| Index | Columns | Type | Reason |
|---|---|---|---|
| PK | [id](file:///d:/IITD/app/%28dashboard%29/upload/page.tsx#76-86) | B-tree | Row lookup |
| `users_firebase_uid_idx` | `firebase_uid` | B-tree UNIQUE | Login sync (every request) |
| `users_email_idx` | `email` | B-tree UNIQUE | Email-based auth lookup |
| `users_deleted_at_idx` | `deleted_at` WHERE NULL | Partial | Filter soft-deleted users |

### `startup_profiles`
| Index | Columns | Type | Reason |
|---|---|---|---|
| PK | [id](file:///d:/IITD/app/%28dashboard%29/upload/page.tsx#76-86) | B-tree | |
| `startup_profiles_user_id_idx` | `user_id` | B-tree UNIQUE | 1:1 join |
| `startup_profiles_sector_stage_idx` | [(sector, stage)](file:///d:/IITD/lib/storage.ts#14-23) | B-tree | Filtering/analytics |

### `decks`
| Index | Columns | Type | Reason |
|---|---|---|---|
| PK | [id](file:///d:/IITD/app/%28dashboard%29/upload/page.tsx#76-86) | B-tree | |
| `decks_user_id_uploaded_at_idx` | [(user_id, uploaded_at DESC)](file:///d:/IITD/lib/storage.ts#14-23) | B-tree | "My decks" list, sorted by date — most frequent query |
| `decks_user_id_status_idx` | [(user_id, status)](file:///d:/IITD/lib/storage.ts#14-23) | B-tree | Filter completed decks for dashboard |
| `decks_status_idx` | [status](file:///d:/IITD/app/%28dashboard%29/analyses/page.tsx#43-55) | B-tree | Admin / monitoring queries |
| `decks_filename_trgm_idx` | `filename` | GIN (pg_trgm) | ILIKE filename search in analyses page |
| `decks_deleted_at_idx` | `deleted_at` WHERE NULL | Partial | Exclude soft-deleted |

### `deck_analyses`
| Index | Columns | Type | Reason |
|---|---|---|---|
| PK | [id](file:///d:/IITD/app/%28dashboard%29/upload/page.tsx#76-86) | B-tree | |
| `deck_analyses_deck_id_idx` | `deck_id` | B-tree UNIQUE | Join from deck, enforces 1:1 |
| `deck_analyses_external_id_idx` | `external_analysis_id` | B-tree UNIQUE | Lookup by AI backend ID |
| `deck_analyses_overall_score_idx` | `overall_score DESC` | B-tree | Sort by score in analyses list |
| `deck_analyses_analyzed_at_idx` | `analyzed_at DESC` | B-tree | Time-series chart on dashboard |

```sql
-- Composite: get all analyses for a user, sorted by date (via deck join)
-- Use the decks_user_id_uploaded_at_idx and join — no extra index needed here

-- GIN index on flags JSONB for future filtering by flag color
CREATE INDEX deck_analyses_flags_gin_idx ON deck_analyses USING GIN (flags);
CREATE INDEX deck_analyses_risk_flags_gin_idx ON deck_analyses USING GIN (risk_flags);
```

### `investment_readiness_results`
| Index | Columns | Type | Reason |
|---|---|---|---|
| PK | [id](file:///d:/IITD/app/%28dashboard%29/upload/page.tsx#76-86) | B-tree | |
| `readiness_user_id_calc_at_idx` | [(user_id, calculated_at DESC)](file:///d:/IITD/lib/storage.ts#14-23) | B-tree | Get latest readiness for user |
| `readiness_analysis_id_idx` | `analysis_id` | B-tree | Many-to-one join to analysis |

### `valuation_results`
| Index | Columns | Type | Reason |
|---|---|---|---|
| PK | [id](file:///d:/IITD/app/%28dashboard%29/upload/page.tsx#76-86) | B-tree | |
| `valuation_user_id_calc_at_idx` | [(user_id, calculated_at DESC)](file:///d:/IITD/lib/storage.ts#14-23) | B-tree | Get latest valuation per user |
| `valuation_sector_stage_idx` | [(sector, stage)](file:///d:/IITD/lib/storage.ts#14-23) | B-tree | Filter valuations by sector/stage (analytics) |

### `audit_log`
| Index | Columns | Type | Reason |
|---|---|---|---|
| PK | [id](file:///d:/IITD/app/%28dashboard%29/upload/page.tsx#76-86) | B-tree (bigserial) | |
| `audit_user_id_created_at_idx` | [(user_id, created_at DESC)](file:///d:/IITD/lib/storage.ts#14-23) | B-tree | User activity history |
| `audit_entity_idx` | [(entity_type, entity_id)](file:///d:/IITD/lib/storage.ts#14-23) | B-tree | Lookup all events for a specific entity |

